    • edit

      public void edit(javafx.event.ActionEvent actionEvent)
      Performs the edit operation. This method is called when the edit button is clicked. It retrieves the input values for student information from the UI fields. It validates the input values and updates the student information in the CSV file. If any of the input fields is empty, it prints an error message. After updating the student information, it closes the page.
      参数:
      actionEvent - the action event triggered by the edit button.
